 Analyst Ratings For Basic Energy Services (NYSE:BAS)
Today, Credit Suisse Group initiated coverage on Basic Energy Services (NYSE:BAS) with a Neutral .
There are 9 hold ratings, 3 buy ratings on the stock.
The current consensus rating on Basic Energy Services (NYSE:BAS) is Hold (Score: 2.25) with a consensus target price of $20.13 per share, a potential 26.68% downside.
