Build Your Future with Basic
Teamwork is the cornerstone of success at Basic Energy Services. If you're looking for a career where you'll work together with a talented and trained team, Basic Energy Services is right for you. At Basic, our policies and employee programs are designed to help our people get the most out of their job and develop their skills.
Basic offers a comprehensive and competitive rewards program, including:

Highly competitive salaries
Benefits programs
Training
Performance-based financial rewards

Take a look at the opportunities we have in your area.


RECRUITING SCAM ADVISORY
Basic Energy Services has become aware of unauthorized individuals who are falsely using the Basic Energy Services name and/or logo in an attempt to solicit fees or private identity information from potential job seekers. These deceptive and unauthorized individuals are soliciting money, promising placement in a position with Basic Energy Services. Please note any communication requesting any amount of money in exchange for employment with Basic Energy Services is fraudulent. These communications do not originate from Basic Energy Services and are not associated with the recruitment process.
Basic Energy Services and its affiliates never charge candidates fees or payments of any kind in order to secure employment. As a precaution, we recommend you do not disclose personal or financial details to anyone as a response to an unsolicited e-mail, social media or dating website request.
Basic Energy Services will never ask for a placement fee or any other fee to expedite the hiring process. If you are contacted by anyone offering employment with Basic Energy Services, you should never be asked to pay a fee for recruiting. Basic personnel will always send e-mail from an identifiable corporate account (ending in @basicenergyservices.com) and never from a public email account, such as Yahoo!™, Gmail™, Google™, or Hotmail™. If you are contacted regarding a fraudulent employment proposal, we encourage you to alert your local law enforcement agency/police authority. You may report fraudulent recruiting emails to This email address is being protected from spambots. You need JavaScript enabled to view it..




“With Basic, you're a part of a team with a proud history of performance.”


 









